org.conqat.engine.core.configuration

Enum EFeatureToggle

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EFeatureToggle>
      • org.conqat.engine.core.configuration.EFeatureToggle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EFeatureToggle>

    public enum EFeatureToggle
extends java.lang.Enum<EFeatureToggle>
    Enum containing all available feature toggles in Teamscale. Feature toggles are enabled via System properties.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • CODE_USAGE_WIDGET

        public static final EFeatureToggle CODE_USAGE_WIDGET
        Enables the code usage widget that shows execution counts per method. This is currently only usable for ABAP projects with direct coverage report upload. The toggle will be removed once code usage analysis supports more languages.

      • BMW_COVERABLE_VOLUME_FILTER

        public static final EFeatureToggle BMW_COVERABLE_VOLUME_FILTER
        Feature configuration for coverage computations (filter coverable volumes).

      • DISABLE_ARCHITECTURE_OVERLAP_CHECK

        public static final EFeatureToggle DISABLE_ARCHITECTURE_OVERLAP_CHECK
        Disable the architecture regex overlap check. Use this if you are using super huge architectures that slow down the architecture analysis significantly.

      • ENABLE_DEMO_LANDING_PAGE

        public static final EFeatureToggle ENABLE_DEMO_LANDING_PAGE
        Enables the landing page that is used for our own demo instance.

      • DISABLE_MEMORY_CHECK
